ATLAS — NOVIZIO VISUAL MEMORY
Load alongside MEMORY.md when active venture is Novizio. Novizio-specific context only — universal rules live in MEMORY.md. 
VENTURE CONTEXT
Aesthetic: editorial minimalism — magazine spread, not catalogue Positioning: premium DTC fashion; clothes that carry meaning 
NOVIZIO VISUAL SYSTEM
Element Rule Lighting Natural, soft, directional — never harsh flash or studio over-lit Background Clean, neutral, textured walls — never busy patterns or branded backdrops Models/People Confident, authentic — not posed or commercial-looking Colour palette Warm neutrals, muted tones — never loud/clashing Composition Negative space allowed; RO thirds; avoid centred catalogue feel Style Editorial lifestyle, street-contextual — never e-commerce flat lay 
WHAT TO ALWAYS AVOID (NOVIZIO)
Stock-photo energy: overly posed, forced smiles Promotional overlays: text burns, price tags, "NEW IN" banners Busy patterns in backgrounds that compete with the garment Oversaturated or high-contrast processed looks Seasonal clichés (Valentine's roses, Christmas tinsel) 
PROMPT ARCHITECTURE NOTES (NOVIZIO)
LEAD_PROMPT_WITH lighting description → model direction → background → mood adjectives
PROVEN DIRECTIONS (NOVIZIO)
Populated from campaigns. EE: [date] — campaign — visual approach — QC pass rate. 
